column2: "I hear that with the masses of Darkers, it's become quite the dangerous situation."
"If Zeno hears that, you know he won't keep it quiet, right? Let's cull some of their numbers before that happens."
"Look, if we cull their numbers, it'll help everyone else, too! So let's do it on our own!"
"Ah, we can give any excuse at this point! Look, come on, let's go without delay!"
